Journal of Plastic Surgery and Hand Surgery (JPHS) is an international, non-profit journal that is flipping to Open Access in 2023. Owned by the Acta Chirurgica Scandinavica Society, JPHS aims to be a leading forum for hand and plastic surgeons from all over the world. Contributions from all parts of the world are welcome.
